i had a chubby/baby face since childhood, I've been bodybuilding for years.. but always focused on my body and never thought about training my face! I've been doing face yoga, neck stretching and chewing gum. It all works a little and help tone some area of the face, but this thing.. is just insane. You can definitely feel the burn after only a few rep. Just don't underestimated the power of your jaw and go for the level 3 or 4 right away. If you are planning to only buy one then get the level 4. If its too hard to start with you can only bite halfway through and you will get the same feel as a lower level. it's expensive but one of the best thing I've bought so far for facial training. My face is more defined, more toned and look more manly than before. I can't recommend this enough.
